Package: READMEBuilder
Title: Guided README Generation for Reproducible Research
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ed", "Ivimey-Cook",
           email = "e.ivimeycook@gmail.com",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1974-1370"))
Description: A Shiny application that walks researchers through building a
    high-quality README file for research datasets and code. Automatically
    describes tabular data columns (ranges, levels, NAs), detects R package
    dependencies from scripts (including pacman, librarian, import and
    groundhog loaders and renv.lock), supports script run-order documentation,
    and exports a formatted README.md. An existing README can be re-imported and
    edited.
